show.description: After surviving a betrayal and a life-altering accident, Anjali wakes up with a new face and no memory of her past. As she falls for her savior Lalit, old enemies like Samar and Manisha resurface, dragging her into a storm of deceit, revenge, and shocking family secrets. Will Anjali’s new identity save her or destroy everyone around her? Watch Now!
